  "Description": {
    "English": "A power storage unit optimized for use in <span class=\"name name-commodity\">starship defensive systems</span>.<br> <br><span class=\"name name-special\">Tritium</span>-fueled capacitors provide quick-release charge for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Deflector Shield</span>, but would overload smaller-scale equipment.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "为<span class=\"name name-commodity\">飞船防御系统</span>而优化的能源储存器。以<br><br><span class=\"name name-special\">氚</span>为燃料的电容器为<span class=\"name name-technology\">偏导护盾</span>提供了快速释放的电荷，但小型装备用它会超载。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种为<span class=\"name name-commodity\">飞船防御系统</span>使用而优化的储能装置。<br><br><span class=\"name name-special\">氚</span>燃料电容能为<span class=\"name name-technology\">偏转护盾</span>提供快速释放的电荷，但会使小型装备过载。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "針對<span class=\"name name-commodity\">太空船防禦系統</span>最佳化設計的電力儲存單位。<br> <br>以<span class=\"name name-special\">氚</span>為能源的電容器，可快速放電為<span class=\"name name-technology\">反射防護罩</span>充能，但用在規模較小的配備就會過載。"
  },
